      "value": "<p>When you reduce a creature to 0 hit points with a melee weapon attack on your turn, you can expend one superiority die to gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can add your superiority die to the damage of the next melee weapon attack you make before the end of your turn.</li>\n<li>Your speed increases by 10 feet until the end of your turn.</li>\n<li>You can make one additional weapon attack as part of the Attack action before the end of your turn.</li>\n</ul>",
